snippet.title: OMEGA 6: The Triangle Stars - Gamescom 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist OMEGA 6: The Triangle Stars on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3128580/

OMEGA 6 The Triangle Stars is an adventure game with 16-bit styling, based on the manga by former Nintendo art director, Takaya Imamura.

Follow Clear River Games on X for updates: http://www.x.com/clearrivergames
